Version 1.6.0

  [ Rony Joao de Sousa ]

  * Build System:
      - Added manual page installation support through Autotools.
      - Introduced an Autotools-based build system.
      - Separated platform-specific socket compatibility helpers to improve portability.

  * Codebase:
      - Refactored hostname resolution into a dedicated resolver component.
      - Removed the obsolete paping_vs2010 directory.
      - Simplified project metadata handling and modernized banner output.
      - Standardized disabled color handling using integer zero values.

  * Documentation
      - Added a project CHANGELOG.
      - Added an AUTHORS file documenting project contributors.
      - Modernized and expanded the paping manual pages.
      - Updated the README.md with refreshed project description and build instructions.

  * Fixes
      - Corrected timeout reporting for refused TCP connections.

  * Networking
      - Added address family awareness during socket creation.
      - Added IPv4 and IPv6 address family selection support.
      - Implemented fallback connection attempts across multiple resolved addresses.
      - Introduced an address-neutral host abstraction layer.
      - Migrated hostname resolution to getaddrinfo(3) with IPv6 support.

